{"interaction":{"author":{"id":208256705,"link":"http://blkmits.tumblr.com/","username":"blkmits"},"content":"godstaff:\nehmzee:\n?If you kill one human unjustly then you have killed all mankind? ? Quran (5:32)\nIt might be because some don?t know about the other cities (sadly, our media is selective) or it unfortunately could be selective humanity/ show of ignorance, but remind others of all the areas that were impacted on this dreadful day. Innocent lives lost, leave your political jargon aside & take a moment. Mourn them all, respect humanity. \n#Beirut. #Baghdad. #Paris. \nIf you believe in the act of prayer, keep them all in your duas. \nAnd remember to speak up about this. Tell those who may not know that these other areas were hurt as well. When they pray for one, tell them to pray for the other. These are all innocent human beings. Please take a moment. \nI can go on about how poisonous Wahhabism/Salafism is or tell you how many #Shia Muslims have been killed by them for centuries (#shiagenocide is real) or how they don?t respect anyone (no matter what religion you are. They hold no tolerance) or how isis is a group of vile beings carrying that ideology. But this is about the victims and the FAMILIES of victims. And that?s all this will be about. \nWe pay respect to the lives lost but also send wishes of courage & patience/sabr for the families who have lost someone. \nMay we also take a moment to pay our respects to all innocent lives that are continuously lost, DAILY. Lives we don?t always hear about. Lives taken by force (murder or terrorism) or by accident/nature (natural disasters). \nWe live a very privileged life. Something that will never go unnoticed by me. I?m fortunate enough to live here while practicing my faith & not being ashamed of my color. Despite the hardships other poc?s & I have experienced here, they are nothing to what the world experiences. As grateful as I am, I refuse to do nothing with this comfort. So don?t hesitate to speak up or to do something for the world. Help others if you have the ability to do so. \nOnce again, thoughts & prayers for the victims who have lost their lives & their families/friends who have been impacted by the tragic events in these cities. \n??\nIf we mourn only those who are like us or are our friends and/or business associates, we are not better than those attacking us.?\nIf we forget we (yes, ?we?) are also responsible of causing a similar suffering to others, but we chose to ignore it because it is convenient for our interests, we are also instruments of destruction because our complacence and silence.\nI?m very sorry for the attacks on France, but I?m equally sorry I ignored the others when they happened, and are still happening, and were silenced by the big media.?\nBoth situations are terrible in the same level, none is more important than the other.\nIt doesn?t matter that part of my ancestry came from Europe. Now we proud ourselves of being??Global?, and so must be our look over the World, not only as a business opportunity or a place to visit from time to time: we must realize the rest of its inhabitants are just like us. with dreams, loves and aspirations. All things we must respect.\nBad people stand in both sides of the fence. Don?t be one of them.\n","created_at":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 12:09:13 +0000","hashtags":["preach","truth"],"id":"1e58c5ad9947aa8083e673ec27fd9d75","link":"http://ehmzee.tumblr.com/post/133171747471","media_type":"photo","received_at":1447675755.0342000,"schema":{"version":3},"subtype":"post","type":"tumblr","tags":["tab7"]},"language":{"tag":"en","tag_extended":"en","confidence":99},"tumblr":{"action":"create","activity":"post","blog":{"description":"Welcome To This Thing Right Here....Yeah....","id":"208256705","is_group_blog":false,"name":"blkmits","title":"hey, that twinkles!","url":"http://blkmits.tumblr.com/"},"blog_name":"blkmits","blogid":"208256705","caption":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://godstaff.tumblr.com/post/13